channel.title: IP Change
channel.description:
Hey, can i get the ip of my server changed from Socioscape.net to 108.168.27.70
It would also be nice if my uptime could be set back to the 90s, but it's cool if not, i'm actually surprised it's so low, since i've been on there for so long. lol

item.title: IP Change
item.dc:creator: @Tom Tom
item.description:
@Tom wrote:

It’s your responsibility to handle these affairs properly, if you wanted your IP to be different you shouldve setup the appropriate network settings so you could change where it resolves to yourself, or took steps to secure your domain, or whatever happened. I can’t do this and the chances MITB will are pretty slim (see: his sig). Sorry.
